Package com.pandora.chemistry.interfaces

Interface Carbon

All Superinterfaces:
SpecieConfiguration, VariableConfiguration
All Known Implementing Classes:
DIC, DOC
public interface Carbon extends SpecieConfiguration
The Carbon interface represents a carbon-based chemical entity in PANDORA chemistry.

Implementing classes may represent various types of carbon compounds. This interface extends the SpecieConfiguration interface, providing configuration details specific to carbon species within the PANDORA chemistry framework.
